{"tid":1279461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武完，輪到和理非嘅回合喇！開設街站行動！阻止建制洗腦行動！","createTime":"2019-07-02T16:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T17:46:37.000Z","uid":136770,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a989e01a93f34c9bce0e421599b002362e08efc7","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"發完一次夢<br />\n勇武並唔能夠長期每日做<br />\n義士都需要休息<br />\n一定要勇武---&gt;和理非---&gt;勇武---&gt;和理非<br />\n輪住出動<br />\n抗爭運動先可以持續<br />\n所以依小弟愚見<br />\n下一步應該係十八區嘅tg grp自發發起街站<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好似今日朗屏咁<br />\n一呼百應</span></span><br />\n自發發起街站向市民解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時<br />\n我地如果見到有建制擺街站！<br />\n我地亦可以用tg grp發起阻止嘅行動！<br />\n喺佢地隔離舉牌騷擾<br />\n令佢地自己收檔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n各位喺tg grp搵到最少20個巴絲先好行動<br />\n人太少好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩事就搵議員！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遍地開花！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0bab935aea172c2c9389d997421452967de8cf2","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d16920cc78d5bbc1ee15f193cd0b7ec99234dfa0","tid":1279461,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:31:08.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"55084657e6a62854c5447235f2b66b68e0671491","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"46eb4b2fe1dc268be35c31b0bea2f92c338e1cdd","tid":1279461,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069b136dd35d15ddd4ffc89fd11e334ed16526fc","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":