":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30cdc99f78f3e22b1df539b190495377e6b03ee","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"幫推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e1fb6d915ad9345374978162cc27fd6026e353","tid":1279461,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc0d9e9dfdaab814f32a833cece268d250ed73e","tid":1279461,"uid":271590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"小弟長文for 中間派，唔知有無用<br />\n<strong><ins>何君堯／梁君堯促懲衝擊無人立法會，莫視撐警集會暴打立法會議員林卓廷</ins></strong><br />\n林卓廷於6月30日行經海富天橋時被何君堯議員撐警集會者包圍，有人以粗言謾罵林，有人高呼「掟佢落去」，有人企圖搶去他手中的電話，向他揮拳令其眼鏡險些飛脫。林卓廷表示，當時「警察擋住都照打」，「有人抓我條腰，有人用長傘插我腹部，被插中兩次；有男人捉住我左手，屈我無名指及尾指；亦有人向我頭部擲水樽」。[註1-3]<br />\n但是撐警隊集會的發起人何君堯無對自己的集會附上責任,無法管理集會,自己舉辦的集會人士以義和團方式襲擊議員[註4],記者[註5,6],跟自己集會的口號《撐警隊、護法治、保安寧》自相矛盾,集會後負責人更訛稱集會井井有條[註7]至今筆者未能找到何君堯對集會事件有任何回應<br />\n梁君堯身為立法會主席對立法會議員被襲視若無睹<br />\n但至立法會在紅旗警示清空後於7月1日被被強闖受損壞,何君堯於7月2日表示， 警方必須嚴懲昨晚衝突立法會的示威者，及找出幕後操控的人，果斷執法。反而無視自己舉辦的集會人士對立法會議員作身體攻擊[註7]<br />\n梁君彥亦先後2天譴責立法會被示威人士暴力充擊[註8,9]<br />\n梁君彥亦明顯對立法會議員的人生安全,特別是泛民,特別輕視,甚至比死物的價值更低<br />\n無人希望有暴力事件,但希望大家不會因立場選擇性譴責,更不應把死物比個別相反政見的人士安全更重要,謝謝<br />\n [註1]林卓廷被襲片段1<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LamCheukTing.Official/videos/vb.534865589914032/2779900445360550/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLamCheukTing.Official%2Fvideos%2Fvb.534865589914032%2F2779900445360550%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=036d16b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LamCheukTing.Official/videos/vb.534865589914032/2779900445360550/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n[註2]林卓廷被襲片段2<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466192-20190702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466192-20190702.htm&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=af686b14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466192-20190702.htm&h=02bc184b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466192-20190702.htm</a><br />\n[註3]林卓廷被襲報道3<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d18ba4ee60383eb54bf6ac4/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d18ba4ee60383eb54bf6ac4%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=2c7a9329\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d18ba4ee60383eb54bf6ac4/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2</a><br />\n[註4]明報-多名記者被吐口水扔泥襲擊 林卓廷遭撐警者圍攻傘插腹<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190701/s00001/1561919304654/%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4%E6%89%94%E6%B3%A5%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E9%81%AD%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E8%80%85%E5%9C%8D%E6%9